pullRequest.title: Update structure of display/layoutEditor classes
pullRequest.bodyText:
This is a merge of work-in-progress on the refactoring of the Layout Editor classes.  See discussions in the jmri-developers list, most recently this thread.
A pre-built version with installers is available from Jenkins for testing.
